WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.486 --> 00:00:01.582
Good morning family.

00:00:01.582 --> 00:00:04.146
I'm excited to be with you again today.

00:00:04.146 --> 00:00:06.959
I have some things I want to say.

00:00:07.943 --> 00:00:14.231
I was driving around this evening and praying like I normally do, and the Lord spoke to me.

00:00:14.528 --> 00:00:21.440
He said, 'Brandon, I want you to make a video entitled What Are You Believing For in 2024?

00:00:21.440 --> 00:00:32.619
' and I want you to talk to the people to encourage them to believe me for the impossible in 2024.

00:00:32.619 --> 00:00:42.760
Believe for the impossible; believe for something so big and so out of your comprehension that it would only take God to move in your circumstances.

00:00:42.760 --> 00:00:47.468
That's what I'm talking about—something so huge, not something easily achievable.

00:00:47.468 --> 00:00:57.192
You can believe for that, but believe for something that without God's intervention, without God's help, it would be impossible to achieve.

00:00:57.887 --> 00:00:59.920
That's what I'm trying to say.

00:00:59.920 --> 00:01:06.804
Every year, my wife and I write down everything we're believing for at the beginning of the year.

00:01:06.804 --> 00:01:11.760
In January, we make the vision plain—the Bible says, 'Write the vision out and make it plain.

00:01:11.760 --> 00:01:15.834
' We write down everything we're believing for.

00:01:17.280 --> 00:01:20.994
For example, right now we're believing for a new home, a bigger house for our family.

00:01:20.994 --> 00:01:22.640
We're believing for Megan.

00:01:24.480 --> 00:01:28.959
It doesn't matter; nothing's too big and nothing's too small.

00:01:28.959 --> 00:01:40.999
Put some small things on there too, but I'm trying to encourage you that the Lord told me to come on here and talk to you all about what you are believing for in 2024.

00:01:40.999 --> 00:01:48.375
Back in October, a man approached me and asked me to pray with him for a spouse.

00:01:49.079 --> 00:01:56.479
I told him, 'Write down every quality of what you're believing for.

00:01:56.479 --> 00:02:03.351
' Be realistic now; you don't have to be flaky with it, like 'I want a blonde bombshell' or whatever your heart's desire is.

00:02:03.351 --> 00:02:12.680
God will give you the desire of your heart, but write down what you're believing for in a Christian spouse.

00:02:20.937 --> 00:02:22.937
Petition the Lord for your new spouse.

00:02:22.937 --> 00:02:27.851
Believe God and petition him for a child or whatever.

00:02:27.851 --> 00:02:29.480
Nothing's too big.

00:02:29.480 --> 00:02:33.340
You may be barren and unable to have a child.

00:02:33.340 --> 00:02:41.849
Write the vision down: 'Lord, I'm believing you and I am petitioning you, Father, for a baby for our home.

00:02:41.849 --> 00:02:44.840
' But first, you need to be married.

00:02:44.840 --> 00:02:53.023
Don't be trying to believe God for a baby outside of wedlock; you need to get married first and make it right.

00:02:53.023 --> 00:02:58.182
Believe God for a baby and he'll bring it to pass.

00:02:58.182 --> 00:03:07.549
If he would bring a baby in the deadness of Sarah's womb with Abraham at 90-something years old, look at what you could have.

00:03:07.549 --> 00:03:17.018
God's no respecter of persons; if he'll bless Abraham with a baby, Isaac, he'll bless you too.

00:03:24.879 --> 00:03:25.181
I believe with all my heart.

00:03:25.181 --> 00:03:31.020
You just lay hands on your stomach and start praying over your womb.

00:03:31.020 --> 00:03:37.680
Start calling that in and saying, 'I call my ovaries to produce.

00:03:48.340 --> 00:03:48.550
I call my uterus to do what it's called to do.

00:03:50.013 --> 00:03:54.015
I call my husband's seed to produce in the name of Jesus.

00:03:54.015 --> 00:04:03.559
' Lay hands on each other and believe God for the supernatural in your life.

00:04:03.559 --> 00:04:10.423
I've seen it happen, and people come back and say, 'We're having a baby.

00:04:10.423 --> 00:04:15.620
' I'm telling you, nothing's too big for our God.

00:04:15.620 --> 00:04:25.709
If you ladies are believing for a husband, write it down, pray over it, and take communion over it.

00:04:25.709 --> 00:04:26.740
Call that husband in.

00:04:26.740 --> 00:04:30.560
Put yourself in a position to meet this person.

00:04:30.560 --> 00:04:38.099
Like I told him, you may need to relocate to a different city.

00:04:38.269 --> 00:04:55.680
The Lord says, 'Hey, your husband or your wife is in such-and-such place,' and you're believing for it, but you live in Kalamazoo and they live somewhere else.

00:04:55.680 --> 00:05:07.680
Put yourself in the position to hear him so you will be in the right place at the right time.

00:05:20.906 --> 00:05:21.048
The steps of the righteous are ordered of the Lord.

00:05:21.048 --> 00:05:29.653
Remember that and believe him that you'll be in the right place at the right time.

00:05:29.653 --> 00:05:32.306
Be on the lookout.

00:05:32.306 --> 00:05:37.006
Expectation brings the manifestation of what you've been believing for.

00:05:37.006 --> 00:05:47.720
He tells me that all the time: 'Brandon, expectation brings your manifestation.

00:05:47.720 --> 00:05:54.319
' Be expecting him to bring the manifestation.

00:05:54.319 --> 00:06:03.1000
He's already paid the price for your healing, for your deliverance, for prosperity, or whatever.

00:06:03.1000 --> 00:06:09.672
But he said that he gives you power to get it done.

00:06:11.184 --> 00:06:13.080
He gives you power to get wealth.

00:06:13.080 --> 00:06:23.135
We have authority in this earth over basically everything because we're seated with him in the heavenlies.

00:06:23.135 --> 00:06:34.559
According to Ephesians, we are seated with him in the heavenlies, far above all principalities and powers and might.

00:06:34.559 --> 00:06:43.107
If we're seated with him and we are joint-heirs with him, nothing's too big.

00:06:47.783 --> 00:06:51.011
That's what I'm trying to tell you all: spouses, babies, finances, houses, whatever.

00:06:51.011 --> 00:06:53.259
But make the vision plain.

00:06:53.259 --> 00:06:54.976
Find scripture to stand on.

00:06:54.976 --> 00:07:01.274
I'm going to say that again: find scripture concerning your circumstances to believe God for.

00:07:01.274 --> 00:07:06.211
You have to have scripture to back your prayers.

00:07:08.970 --> 00:07:12.289
Don't just be praying flipping things, because you need word to back it.

00:07:19.566 --> 00:07:27.752
You have to find word to back what you're believing for so that you know it lines up with the word of God.

00:07:27.752 --> 00:07:32.298
He doesn't want anybody to be alone or barren.

00:07:32.298 --> 00:07:38.391
He said, 'The fruit of your womb will be blessed.

00:07:38.391 --> 00:07:41.399
' My vine will not cast its fruit before the time.

00:07:41.399 --> 00:07:52.720
If you have problems with miscarriages, my vine will not cast fruit before the time, and he said he rebukes the devourer for your sake.

00:08:01.726 --> 00:08:05.370
The devourer is eating your seed, your fruit of your womb, and you have authority over that by praying and commissioning your womb not to cast fruit before its time.

00:08:05.370 --> 00:08:06.759
That's in Deuteronomy 28.

00:08:06.759 --> 00:08:10.085
Believe that and stand on the word.

00:08:10.085 --> 00:08:17.532
I'm just trying to throw some things out there of what you could believe for in 2024.

00:08:20.493 --> 00:08:29.866
I felt a lot of people are believing for children, spouses, or finances because they're broke and don't have enough to make it paycheck to paycheck.

00:08:29.866 --> 00:08:42.449
God is not a paycheck-to-paycheck God; he is an overflow God that is exceedingly abundantly above all that you dare ask or think according to the power that worketh in you.

00:08:53.775 --> 00:08:54.320
He is an overflow God.

00:08:55.845 --> 00:09:05.560
You may not own a home; you may live in a rental house or a lease, and you want your own home.

00:09:17.680 --> 00:09:17.896
I drive around and I dream all the time.

00:09:18.112 --> 00:09:35.260
I drive around and look at homes and say, 'Father, I know that you're the God that owns the cattle on a thousand hills, and I know that you produce wealth in my hands.

00:09:35.260 --> 00:09:57.480
Father, you'll take care of my family and we'll have a good house, a place to lay our head at night that's good and insulated, protects us in the winter, and is good in the summer.

00:09:57.480 --> 00:10:19.920
Lord, I need a bigger home so my daughter can have her own room, because my oldest one needs her own room because she has special needs.

00:10:19.920 --> 00:10:33.190
' I thank you, Lord, that not only you're going to heal Megan, but God, you'll provide a bedroom for my little one.

00:10:33.190 --> 00:10:42.188
That's what I do; I pray for it and God gives you the desires of your heart.

00:10:42.188 --> 00:10:48.631
Ladies and gentlemen, I believe with all my heart he's not broke.

00:10:48.631 --> 00:10:58.520
He's not up there going, 'Well, I got to talk to Jesus and see if our bank accounts are okay to provide a new home.

00:10:58.520 --> 00:11:12.729
' He doesn't go, 'Well, no, we're a little low up here in heaven; we got to cash in one of our gold bricks or some pearls because we're a little low.

00:11:12.729 --> 00:11:15.399
' No, he's an overflow God.

00:11:15.399 --> 00:11:17.080
He has more than enough for you.

00:11:17.080 --> 00:11:23.320
He'll give you a creative idea to get wealth.

00:11:26.453 --> 00:11:28.420
All you have to do is switch over your stinking thinking.

00:11:28.420 --> 00:11:38.000
It's your thinking; if it's poverty-minded, you think, 'Well, God doesn't love me, he's not going to take care of me.

00:11:38.000 --> 00:11:40.300
' No, he loves you.

00:11:50.680 --> 00:11:50.875
Faith works by love.

00:11:55.981 --> 00:12:01.630
The Lord said, 'Brandon, there's people on your channel that are asking me why their faith is not working.

00:12:01.630 --> 00:12:04.809
' He said, 'Faith works by love.

00:12:04.809 --> 00:12:22.519
' If you want to know why your prayers aren't getting answered when you're petitioning him for things like healing, check your love walk.

00:12:22.519 --> 00:12:34.468
If your love walk isn't right with him and you're treating people like trash—your spouse, your kids, your neighbor—love...

00:12:38.024 --> 00:12:41.345
faith works by love.

00:12:45.720 --> 00:12:45.1000
It's that simple.

00:12:45.1000 --> 00:12:56.160
I automatically go to my love gauge, and if it isn't full and you aren't walking in love, maybe that's why your faith isn't working.

00:12:56.160 --> 00:12:58.302
It's so true and real.

00:13:02.352 --> 00:13:13.290
The Bible even talks about how if you aren't honoring your wife and treating her with respect, the Lord doesn't hear your prayers.

00:13:26.589 --> 00:13:26.904
I don't have the exact street address for that chapter and verse, but it's in the Bible.

00:13:26.904 --> 00:13:28.165
Google it.

00:13:28.165 --> 00:13:37.120
I'll have my son find it and put it in the video right here.

00:13:37.120 --> 00:13:44.391
If you don't honor your wife and treat her right, your prayers aren't going to be heard.

00:13:44.391 --> 00:13:54.239
You've got to honor your wives, husbands; you've got to treat them with respect and pray for them.

00:13:54.239 --> 00:14:01.579
If you want your prayers to be answered, you've got to walk in love and goodness.

00:14:01.579 --> 00:14:05.034
People do you wrong all the time.

00:14:11.750 --> 00:14:17.493
I have a problem sometimes holding a grudge, and the Lord tells me, 'Love takes no account of a suffered wrong, Brandon.

00:14:22.1000 --> 00:14:23.239
You got to let it go.

00:14:23.239 --> 00:14:32.499
' Love takes no account of a suffered wrong; love is patient, love is kind.

00:14:32.499 --> 00:14:39.285
Look at all the things the Bible says love is.

00:14:39.285 --> 00:14:47.813
That's where you have to base where your faith is at; it's like a gauge.

00:14:47.813 --> 00:15:00.679
First John 4 says, 'Beloved, let us love one another, for love is of God; and everyone that loveth is born of God and knoweth God.

00:15:00.679 --> 00:15:07.129
He that loveth not knoweth not God, for God is love.

00:15:07.129 --> 00:15:17.759
' Then it says in other scriptures that perfect love casteth out all fear because fear has torment.

00:15:17.759 --> 00:15:29.839
There's so much about putting your faith in motion, but love is the fuel behind your faith.

00:15:29.839 --> 00:15:33.056
It's like putting jet fuel in a jet.

00:15:43.173 --> 00:15:43.560
The jet's not going to take off and do what it has to do without it.

00:15:43.560 --> 00:15:55.354
When you operate in faith, you put your love walk and love fuel in there to make the jet go.

00:15:55.680 --> 00:16:00.010
I'm trying my best to explain this to you all.

00:16:03.740 --> 00:16:05.400
Going back, write the vision down and make it plain.

00:16:11.033 --> 00:16:11.440
What are you believing for in 2024?

00:16:11.440 --> 00:16:13.659
Believe big; you're thinking too small.

00:16:21.070 --> 00:16:21.375
Get your love walk right and write down the vision.

00:16:21.375 --> 00:16:28.043
You're going to be amazed at how many things God brought to pass in your life.

00:16:28.043 --> 00:16:35.970
I write it down, I anoint that vision with oil, I call it in, and I plead the blood of Jesus over it.

00:16:50.994 --> 00:16:51.309
I take communion, which is a covenant between me and the Father.

00:16:51.309 --> 00:16:59.924
He said, 'Do this in remembrance of me.

00:16:59.924 --> 00:17:07.337
' When you eat that cracker, you partake of him.

00:17:20.088 --> 00:17:20.319
I believe with all my heart, 'Father, you flow through these veins; you are inside of me.

00:17:20.319 --> 00:17:25.320
I hear you clearly because you dwell on the inside of me.

00:17:25.320 --> 00:17:27.731
' I am wall-to-wall Holy Ghost.

00:17:27.731 --> 00:17:31.039
He fills all of me.

00:17:31.039 --> 00:17:43.640
If you have a problem with smoking and you're believing to be free from tobacco or for a healing, write it down and call it in.

00:17:43.640 --> 00:17:48.711
Faith calls those things that be not as though they were.

00:17:48.711 --> 00:17:50.116
Find scriptures.

00:17:50.116 --> 00:17:53.646
'I call myself delivered from nicotine.

00:17:53.646 --> 00:17:57.344
I'm delivered from drugs or pornography.

00:17:57.344 --> 00:18:02.209
I am free from bondage from satanical addictions.

00:18:02.209 --> 00:18:04.511
I speak to strongholds.

00:18:04.511 --> 00:18:08.191
I am free from generational strongholds.

00:18:08.191 --> 00:18:16.342
' The Bible says, 'For whom the Son has set free is free indeed.

00:18:16.342 --> 00:18:19.333
' You are free.

00:18:23.640 --> 00:18:25.050
You have to believe that, but find scriptures for what you're believing for.

00:18:25.050 --> 00:18:40.142
Most people say, 'I don't have any scriptures I'm standing on,' and you're not going to receive anything because it's the word that backs the prayer.

00:18:41.480 --> 00:18:46.123
That's what puts faith in motion with love.

00:18:56.120 --> 00:18:56.413
It's like a formula.

00:18:56.413 --> 00:19:07.862
You've got to put the love walk first—put the fuel in the jet—but you've got to find word to stand on.

00:19:07.862 --> 00:19:11.705
It puts the wind in the sail.

00:19:11.705 --> 00:19:16.220
Get the word down inside of you, ladies and gentlemen.

00:19:16.220 --> 00:19:20.299
That's what's going to change your life.

00:19:20.299 --> 00:19:25.600
You know the truth, and the truth will set you free.

00:19:33.120 --> 00:19:33.474
Not all this stuff everybody talks about regarding casting out devils.

00:19:38.527 --> 00:19:47.720
You aren't going to stay free if you don't have the word inside of you.

00:19:47.720 --> 00:19:56.560
That devil's going to come back with eight more of his buddies and you're going to be bound even worse.

00:19:56.560 --> 00:20:05.685
Jesus said, 'Go and sin no more, lest a worse thing come upon you.

00:20:05.685 --> 00:20:24.634
' He's trying to warn you: stay out of sin, strife, and compromise.

00:20:24.634 --> 00:20:37.987
Seek the Lord with all your heart.

00:20:37.987 --> 00:21:06.480
His word says that the eyes of the Lord run to and fro throughout the whole world looking for a heart who's perfect toward him.

00:21:06.480 --> 00:21:15.475
Let his eyes fall upon you today.

00:21:41.780 --> 00:21:42.075
Be that vessel that can be used by God in these last days.

00:21:42.075 --> 00:21:45.629
Get that word inside of you.

00:21:45.629 --> 00:21:52.469
People died for you to be able to read that.

00:21:52.469 --> 00:21:58.056
They sacrificed their lives; that's how important it was.

00:21:58.056 --> 00:22:09.337
It's the only thing the devil tries to distract you from: getting in prayer and getting in the word.

00:22:09.337 --> 00:22:16.440
Find verses that you understand—use the Amplified or the New Living Translation.

00:22:16.440 --> 00:22:27.370
If you don't understand the King James, that's fine; get something you can read.

00:22:27.370 --> 00:22:32.029
Your life will be changed.

00:22:32.029 --> 00:22:37.855
I hope that made some sense.

00:22:37.855 --> 00:22:45.950
Believe for the impossible because God wants to do something big today.

00:22:45.950 --> 00:22:53.640
He loves you so much and has a plan for your life.

00:22:53.640 --> 00:23:06.969
'Beloved, I wish above all things that thou mayest prosper and be in health, even as thy soul prospers.

00:23:06.969 --> 00:23:15.000
' He wants you to be prosperous in your soul and your family.

00:23:15.000 --> 00:23:22.360
Prosperity is being blessed; your children are blessed, not sick or strung out on drugs.

00:23:22.360 --> 00:23:26.389
He wants you to have a successful home.

00:23:39.880 --> 00:23:40.253
Jesus loves you and I love you guys.

00:23:40.253 --> 00:23:43.547
Thank you for watching me.

00:23:43.547 --> 00:23:45.924
It's a blessing.

00:23:45.924 --> 00:24:05.182
I still shake myself all the time because I used to believe for ministry for years, and to see that God would use me...

00:24:17.462 --> 00:24:17.737
I'm thankful he's brought all this to pass.

00:24:17.737 --> 00:24:30.000
This was one of the things I wrote on my paper for years: that I could help people.

00:24:30.000 --> 00:24:50.408
Lord, I just thank you right now in the name of Jesus for every person believing for the impossible, for you make all things possible to him that believe.

00:24:50.408 --> 00:24:54.211
No matter how big or small, you're faithful.

00:25:07.848 --> 00:25:08.204
I speak to their circumstances and I call those things that be not as though they were.

00:25:08.204 --> 00:25:12.910
Someone's spouse is going to become radically saved in 2024.

00:25:12.910 --> 00:25:18.040
The Lord just told me they're coming in.

00:25:18.040 --> 00:25:21.968
Your spouse is coming to Jesus.

00:25:21.968 --> 00:25:27.387
The harvest is coming in for souls in 2024.

00:25:27.387 --> 00:25:30.098
I'm calling in the wayward children.

00:25:30.098 --> 00:25:34.248
I'm calling in the healings that seem impossible.

00:25:34.248 --> 00:25:42.120
Those days of 'hope deferred makes the heart sick' are done.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.350
Let the healing power of Jesus flow through them from the top of their head to the soles of their feet.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
Father, I thank you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
From cancers to diabetes, there is always a 'suddenly.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
' We call the 'suddenly' to happen now.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
faith calls those things that be not as though they were now.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
We call them delivered.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.950
There is overflow coming to your house: creative ideas to get wealth, raises, bonuses, benefits, and sales.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
Interest and returns, rebates, gifts, and surprises.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
Finding money and bills paid off.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
Believe it all; there's overflow coming to your house.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
Expectation brings the manifestation.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
God's got you in the palm of his hand and he loves you so much.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
Thank you for being a part of our little YouTube channel.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
Please like, subscribe, and click the notification bell.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
God's got an amazing plan for your future.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Jesus loves you so much, and we will see you next time.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
Have a blessed day.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Bye-bye.
